I’m using the following script to push an event to Google Tag Manager, then I load tracking scripts based on user consent.

```_hsq.push([
    "addPrivacyConsentListener",
    function(consent) {
      if (consent.allowed === true) {
        dataLayer.push({ event: "HubSpot-consent-true" });
      } else if (consent.allowed === false) {
        dataLayer.push({ event: "HubSpot-consent-false" });
      }
    }
  ]);```
